WEBVTT

01:40.380 --> 01:48.740
[You are My Fateful Love]
[EP08]

01:50.979 --> 01:51.500
Look over there.

01:52.220 --> 01:52.660
The flowers are nice.

01:52.660 --> 01:53.220
Coming.

01:59.819 --> 02:00.338
Hello.

02:00.339 --> 02:00.899
Hi.

02:00.899 --> 02:01.940
Are you Ms. Ruan,

02:01.940 --> 02:02.500
Ruan Yu?

02:02.860 --> 02:03.380
Yes, I am.

02:03.380 --> 02:04.259
I'm the property manager

02:04.259 --> 02:05.020
for this complex.

02:05.100 --> 02:05.699
Here's the thing.

02:05.740 --> 02:06.619
Early this morning,

02:06.619 --> 02:07.500
there was a drunk guy

02:07.500 --> 02:08.580
lurking downstairs from your place.

02:08.940 --> 02:10.300
He didn't bother you, did he?

02:10.300 --> 02:10.940
A drunk guy?

02:11.940 --> 02:12.780
Bother me?

02:13.819 --> 02:14.380
No.

02:15.380 --> 02:15.899
Good.

02:16.340 --> 02:17.060
Make sure to lock

02:17.060 --> 02:18.259
your doors and windows at night.

02:18.380 --> 02:18.979
Stay safe.

02:19.620 --> 02:20.180
We'll also

02:20.180 --> 02:21.180
step up security patrols

02:21.180 --> 02:22.340
around the complex.

02:22.780 --> 02:23.780
If anything happens,

02:24.019 --> 02:24.780
just give us a call

02:24.780 --> 02:25.579
right away.

02:25.699 --> 02:26.259
Then I'm leaving.

02:26.979 --> 02:27.739
Hold on a sec.

02:28.900 --> 02:30.620
That drunk guy,

02:30.620 --> 02:31.419
have you found him?

02:31.940 --> 02:33.060
He was taken away last night.

02:34.380 --> 02:34.940
Good to hear.

02:36.019 --> 02:37.660
Honestly, it was kinda creepy.

02:38.019 --> 02:38.819
He was right downstairs

02:38.819 --> 02:39.900
from your place,

02:40.259 --> 02:42.340
pacing around that tree,

02:42.579 --> 02:43.539
talking to himself one minute,

02:43.539 --> 02:44.620
then singing and dancing the next.

02:45.620 --> 02:46.979
[What kind of sick behavior is that?]

02:49.819 --> 02:50.699
Li Shican,

02:51.060 --> 02:52.019
I can do it too!

02:58.380 --> 02:59.340
Is Li Shican

02:59.340 --> 03:00.660
that famous now?

03:02.100 --> 03:03.660
Which crazy male fan

03:03.660 --> 03:05.620
is out there fanboying at this hour?

03:08.380 --> 03:09.579
Was that when it happened?

03:10.739 --> 03:12.100
Why would

03:12.259 --> 03:13.259
Li Shican's fan

03:13.259 --> 03:14.019
come to my place?

03:15.340 --> 03:16.060
Thanks.

03:16.380 --> 03:17.620
I'll get going then.

03:18.100 --> 03:18.660
-Thank you.
-Bye.

03:24.340 --> 03:25.500
A drunk guy.

03:25.859 --> 03:26.900
Kinda scary.

03:33.060 --> 03:33.859
Late-night drinks

03:33.859 --> 03:34.579
with someone.

03:34.819 --> 03:35.979
Nothing special.

03:36.340 --> 03:37.019
Just one word.

03:37.299 --> 03:39.180
S-L-

03:39.620 --> 03:40.979
E-E-

03:40.979 --> 03:42.699
P-Y.

03:42.940 --> 03:43.579
Sleepy.

03:45.060 --> 03:46.299
Mr. Liu is pretty funny.

03:58.340 --> 03:59.220
Gentlemen,

03:59.620 --> 04:00.780
can I ask you something?

04:00.819 --> 04:01.940
Do you know

04:01.940 --> 04:03.340
how to deal with a creep?

04:03.620 --> 04:04.500
If some drunk guy

04:04.500 --> 04:06.060
harasses you in the middle of the night,

04:06.259 --> 04:07.259
what should you do?

04:19.180 --> 04:20.660
What's got you so happy, Mao?

04:20.819 --> 04:22.100
Don't ask me.

04:22.500 --> 04:23.739
Ask the man himself.

04:23.739 --> 04:24.539
Ask Huaisong.

04:26.140 --> 04:27.499
Is our firm

04:27.499 --> 04:28.299
that slow right now?

04:29.299 --> 04:30.020
We don't have any

04:30.020 --> 04:30.780
legal consultation cases?

04:31.140 --> 04:31.979
If that's the case, Liu Mao,

04:32.419 --> 04:33.739
we might not need to keep our interns.

04:33.739 --> 04:34.739
We do!

04:34.739 --> 04:36.220
I've got over a dozen cases today.

04:36.220 --> 04:37.460
I... I'll get back to work.

04:38.100 --> 04:38.900
-Ms. Zhang.
-I'm free.

04:39.299 --> 04:40.179
Why don't you tell me?

04:40.739 --> 04:41.739
How are you free?

04:41.739 --> 04:43.059
You've got so many domestic violence cases,

04:43.059 --> 04:43.900
and then all those

04:43.900 --> 04:44.739
disputes at construction sites.

04:45.220 --> 04:46.020
I don't want to waste your time

04:46.460 --> 04:47.499
with my small problem.

04:47.499 --> 04:48.220
I'll head back now.

04:50.179 --> 04:51.179
How small?

04:51.619 --> 04:52.379
since you put it that way,

04:52.820 --> 04:53.979
I'm even more curious.

04:54.820 --> 04:55.340
Ms. Zhang,

04:57.419 --> 04:58.260
curious?

04:58.780 --> 04:59.539
Let me show you.

05:05.739 --> 05:06.260
Check this out.

05:06.260 --> 05:07.580
Does the guy

05:08.059 --> 05:08.900
in this video

05:09.340 --> 05:09.939
look kinda like

05:09.939 --> 05:10.939
Mr. Xu?

05:24.700 --> 05:25.260
You got this.

05:26.499 --> 05:27.059
You got this.

05:28.020 --> 05:28.700
Xu Huaisong,

05:30.539 --> 05:31.179
you can do it.

05:41.700 --> 05:43.299
We need to stay rational.

05:44.539 --> 05:46.379
Yes, rational.

05:48.179 --> 05:49.499
Image matters.

05:49.700 --> 05:50.539
We can't go into

05:50.539 --> 05:51.539
battle unprepared.

05:52.140 --> 05:53.299
So think about

05:53.539 --> 05:55.059
those keywords:

05:56.059 --> 05:56.739
Elegant.

06:00.140 --> 06:00.700
Elegant.

06:02.780 --> 06:03.419
Aloof.

06:03.859 --> 06:04.260
Yeah.

06:04.260 --> 06:05.220
She likes that.

06:06.460 --> 06:07.140
Aloof.

06:08.739 --> 06:09.379
Aloof.

06:10.460 --> 06:11.900
There's one more besides aloof.

06:14.419 --> 06:15.140
Singing and dancing.

06:18.580 --> 06:21.100
Li Shican, singing and dancing.

06:23.900 --> 06:25.059
How hard can it be?

06:26.499 --> 06:27.700
How hard can it be?

06:28.220 --> 06:30.100
If Li Shican can sing and dance,

06:30.100 --> 06:31.100
I can too!

06:34.020 --> 06:34.820
Li Shican,

06:35.260 --> 06:36.140
I can do it too!

06:47.700 --> 06:48.220
Property management?

06:48.419 --> 06:49.499
I just got up to use the bathroom

06:49.499 --> 06:50.100
and noticed someone downstairs

06:50.100 --> 06:50.900
who's totally hammered.

06:50.979 --> 06:52.020
He's acting crazy.

06:52.179 --> 06:53.179
Come over quick.

06:53.700 --> 06:54.660
Hurry up.

07:15.859 --> 07:16.419
Elegant.

07:17.020 --> 07:17.539
Aloof.

07:18.340 --> 07:18.979
Singing and dancing.

07:19.499 --> 07:20.100
I can do this.

07:22.499 --> 07:23.100
Ruan Yu,

07:23.859 --> 07:24.460
here I come.

07:26.700 --> 07:27.299
Where are you going?

07:28.059 --> 07:29.059
No time to ask.

07:29.340 --> 07:30.260
Just drag him away.

07:30.700 --> 07:31.140
What?

07:31.619 --> 07:32.140
What are you doing?

07:32.580 --> 07:33.059
-Wait!
-Come on.

07:33.419 --> 07:33.820
What...

07:38.539 --> 07:39.419
Not kinda.

07:40.660 --> 07:41.859
At least a little, right?

07:41.859 --> 07:42.859
Barely.

07:44.419 --> 07:46.100
A little bit, right?

07:47.340 --> 07:49.059
I say, he looks just like him.

07:49.939 --> 07:51.059
Good moves.

07:51.059 --> 07:52.260
Shame you aren't a dancer.

07:52.340 --> 07:53.100
What a shame.

07:53.299 --> 07:54.460
Even Ms. Zhang says it's a shame.

07:59.260 --> 07:59.939
Ruan Yu. Ruan Yu.

08:01.979 --> 08:03.340
I've asked

08:03.340 --> 08:04.900
a cop I know.

08:05.340 --> 08:05.939
That guy

08:05.939 --> 08:07.379
in your neighborhood last night

08:07.739 --> 08:08.580
was just

08:08.580 --> 08:10.340
some heartbroken dude.

08:11.059 --> 08:12.020
He drank too much

08:12.460 --> 08:13.859
and lost his mind.

08:15.340 --> 08:16.499
The cops

08:16.499 --> 08:18.140
gave him a talking-to.

08:18.140 --> 08:19.140
Don't worry.

08:19.580 --> 08:20.780
He's probably

08:21.660 --> 08:23.100
learned his lesson by now.

08:25.539 --> 08:26.140
Relax.

08:26.140 --> 08:26.939
Nothing else will happen.

08:33.900 --> 08:34.900
Talk about your bad timing.

08:35.820 --> 08:36.539
You were just about to

08:36.859 --> 08:38.020
ring her bell, and you got caught.

08:39.299 --> 08:39.859
Too bad.

08:42.379 --> 08:43.259
Not too bad.

08:44.259 --> 08:45.220
It's a good thing.

08:45.979 --> 08:46.580
How so?

08:47.940 --> 08:49.259
With Mr. Xu,

08:49.779 --> 08:51.100
love's like a courtroom.

08:51.420 --> 08:52.420
He has to avoid

08:52.420 --> 08:53.739
any ill-timed recklessness.

08:53.820 --> 08:54.979
He'll never rush to slam the gravel

08:54.979 --> 08:56.259
until it's time to close the case.

08:56.580 --> 08:57.340
But love

08:58.460 --> 09:00.940
is not a courtroom

09:00.940 --> 09:02.139
A courtroom is about evidence.

09:02.139 --> 09:03.220
Love is about tug-of-war.

09:03.220 --> 09:04.259
Any relationship

09:04.259 --> 09:05.739
is a tug-of-war.

09:06.340 --> 09:07.739
All's fair in love and war.

09:10.460 --> 09:11.139
I'm off.

09:11.180 --> 09:12.739
Time to hit the construction site.

09:13.220 --> 09:13.739
Good advice.

09:13.739 --> 09:14.180
Yeah, Mr. Xu.

09:14.180 --> 09:15.139
Let me say something.

09:15.139 --> 09:15.979
I really think

09:16.259 --> 09:17.019
when it comes to dating,

09:17.019 --> 09:17.540
you can't treat it

09:17.540 --> 09:18.460
like a case.

09:18.460 --> 09:19.580
If you wait until you're sure

09:19.580 --> 09:20.619
to win before you act,

09:20.859 --> 09:21.820
won't someone else

09:21.820 --> 09:23.259
snatch her

09:23.259 --> 09:23.700
up first?

09:26.220 --> 09:26.979
You're not leaving?

09:27.619 --> 09:28.019
I... I...

09:28.300 --> 09:28.979
I shouldn't have said that.

09:28.979 --> 09:30.060
I'll get back to work now.

09:30.420 --> 09:30.820
Bye.

09:32.580 --> 09:34.139
He's getting cuter and cuter.

09:41.940 --> 09:42.899
Until I'm sure to win...

09:44.700 --> 09:45.940
[He's probably]

09:46.779 --> 09:48.340
[learned his lesson by now.]

09:49.019 --> 09:49.739
[Relax.]

09:49.739 --> 09:50.619
[Nothing else will happen.]

09:55.540 --> 09:57.019
Nothing can't be overcome.

09:57.220 --> 09:58.700
Just can't go back anymore.

10:00.019 --> 10:01.019
What a cheesy line.

10:01.379 --> 10:02.259
When did I accidentally

10:02.259 --> 10:02.979
like that?

10:12.580 --> 10:13.899
The anti-plagiarism report
is ready to finalize.

10:14.300 --> 10:15.540
Pre-litigation work is basically

10:15.540 --> 10:16.700
done at this point.

10:20.379 --> 10:21.300
At least he didn't nitpick

10:21.300 --> 10:22.899
my Chapter 23.

10:25.619 --> 10:26.340
Adults

10:27.019 --> 10:27.779
know how to

10:27.779 --> 10:29.300
leave each other some dignity.

10:42.379 --> 10:43.659
Mr. Liu, Mr. Xu,

10:44.019 --> 10:45.060
thank you both for all your

10:45.060 --> 10:46.220
hard work on my case.

10:46.580 --> 10:47.820
If you're free tonight,

10:47.940 --> 10:49.019
let me take you out to dinner.

10:50.820 --> 10:52.220
Looks like Ruan Yu's doing fine.

10:53.580 --> 10:54.300
She didn't see that

10:54.300 --> 10:55.340
amazing video of yours.

10:57.940 --> 10:58.460
Alright.

10:59.979 --> 11:01.060
Let's do Cantonese.

11:03.659 --> 11:04.540
Is this place okay?

11:05.180 --> 11:06.379
Mr. Xu is recovering,

11:06.580 --> 11:07.700
so something light is better.

11:09.540 --> 11:10.940
If Ruan Yu knew

11:11.100 --> 11:12.580
how Mr. Xu was

11:12.580 --> 11:14.379
acting last night...

11:17.619 --> 11:19.060
Ruan Yu, sorry.

11:19.499 --> 11:20.820
I've got a blind date tonight,

11:21.340 --> 11:22.100
so I can't make it.

11:22.820 --> 11:24.940
You and Mr. Xu enjoy.

11:29.859 --> 11:30.659
Him and me?

11:32.859 --> 11:33.499
So?

11:35.060 --> 11:35.940
Got your back, right?

11:38.300 --> 11:39.859
Is that a real blind date?

11:39.859 --> 11:41.019
Of course it is.

11:43.340 --> 11:44.460
Let's both do our best,

11:45.139 --> 11:46.060
see who gets there first.

11:46.300 --> 11:47.060
It better be.

11:49.420 --> 11:50.420
A piece of advice for you.

11:52.100 --> 11:53.899
Don't drink when you

11:54.460 --> 11:55.540
have dinner with Ruan Yu.

11:56.139 --> 11:56.739
You can't

11:56.739 --> 11:58.659
handle your liquor well.

12:18.899 --> 12:20.259
It feels a bit strange

12:20.820 --> 12:22.180
without Mr. Liu here.

12:25.340 --> 12:26.700
Braised pork intestine.

12:27.619 --> 12:28.859
Someone aloof

12:28.859 --> 12:29.779
wouldn't eat this.

12:30.340 --> 12:31.300
Crispy roast duck.

12:32.220 --> 12:33.340
He just got out of the hospital.

12:33.619 --> 12:34.499
He probably shouldn't eat

12:34.499 --> 12:35.460
something this greasy.

12:36.139 --> 12:36.859
But this roast duck

12:36.859 --> 12:38.019
looks so good.

12:39.700 --> 12:40.899
Century egg and lean pork congee.

12:41.899 --> 12:42.979
Cured stuff is

12:43.139 --> 12:44.019
hard on the stomach.

12:44.220 --> 12:45.580
Braised Chicken Feet.

12:45.940 --> 12:46.779
Need to use hands.

12:47.300 --> 12:48.379
Not graceful enough.

12:49.060 --> 12:50.060
Beef's no good either.

12:50.060 --> 12:51.139
Too hard to digest.

12:51.580 --> 12:52.379
Garlic's no good.

12:53.060 --> 12:53.899
Smell's too strong.

12:54.420 --> 12:55.619
Seafood's no good either.

12:56.139 --> 12:56.899
What if his stomach

12:56.899 --> 12:57.940
is inflamed?

12:58.499 --> 13:00.180
Chicken cartilage, no good.

13:01.100 --> 13:02.300
Too noisy to eat.

13:07.379 --> 13:07.940
Ready to order?

13:21.420 --> 13:22.340
After all that,

13:22.340 --> 13:24.019
they only ordered two bowls of congee?

13:24.540 --> 13:25.580
A guy can be average-looking

13:25.580 --> 13:27.259
but can't be stingy.

13:27.499 --> 13:29.180
Looks don't pay the bills.

13:31.300 --> 13:31.859
Mr. Xu,

13:32.139 --> 13:33.259
you don't have
to save me money.

13:33.580 --> 13:34.700
We can order more.

13:35.499 --> 13:36.019
It's good enough.

13:41.060 --> 13:42.019
Have there been more trolls

13:42.019 --> 13:42.899
harassing you lately?

13:44.060 --> 13:44.659
No.

13:44.940 --> 13:45.700
Ever since I sent out

13:45.700 --> 13:46.340
that cease and desist,

13:46.340 --> 13:47.259
it's died down.

13:50.259 --> 13:51.100
Have you still been

13:51.619 --> 13:53.019
checking comments much?

13:55.499 --> 13:56.019
Occasionally.

13:56.659 --> 13:58.060
I've been handling it a lot better.

13:58.460 --> 13:59.379
Don't worry, Mr. Xu.

14:00.499 --> 14:00.979
Good.

14:08.899 --> 14:10.019
A lot of people think

14:10.979 --> 14:12.340
it's no big deal to like a post

14:12.340 --> 14:13.499
or leave a comment online.

14:14.139 --> 14:15.420
But when there's a lawsuit,

14:15.940 --> 14:16.659
those actions

14:16.659 --> 14:17.859
can be seen as reflecting

14:17.859 --> 14:18.580
a client's position.

14:21.460 --> 14:22.820
I did accidentally like a post.

14:23.100 --> 14:24.220
But I unliked it right away.

14:25.060 --> 14:26.139
Would that affect the case?

14:27.499 --> 14:28.180
What did you like?

14:29.899 --> 14:30.820
The trial is coming up.

14:31.139 --> 14:32.100
We can't afford any complications.

14:34.580 --> 14:35.619
But it wasn't really

14:35.700 --> 14:36.659
related to the case.

14:37.259 --> 14:38.180
It was just some

14:38.180 --> 14:39.300
melodramatic post.

14:40.899 --> 14:41.739
Then why'd you

14:42.659 --> 14:43.659
unlike it?

14:47.259 --> 14:48.259
It was something about

14:48.340 --> 14:49.820
never being able to go back.

14:50.060 --> 14:51.259
I thought it was too corny.

14:52.060 --> 14:52.739
I mean, I write

14:52.739 --> 14:53.619
romance novels,

14:54.139 --> 14:54.940
but even I can't

14:54.940 --> 14:55.899
handle that style.

15:00.580 --> 15:01.100
Good to know.

15:02.379 --> 15:03.300
What did you say, Mr. Xu?

15:11.259 --> 15:12.060
I said,

15:13.420 --> 15:15.460
good to know.

15:18.340 --> 15:19.499
Let's eat.

15:24.779 --> 15:26.700
[You're the one who started chatting with me.]

15:30.820 --> 15:31.659
Excuse me, Mr. Xu.

15:36.420 --> 15:37.659
Ruan Yu, check out the video.

15:37.739 --> 15:39.180
That drunk guy from the other night

15:39.580 --> 15:40.820
was so hilarious.

15:57.979 --> 15:58.859
This drunk guy

15:58.979 --> 16:00.220
kinda looks like...

16:05.220 --> 16:05.859
Drunk guy?

16:08.139 --> 16:08.739
Looks like me?

16:10.300 --> 16:10.979
No.

16:11.340 --> 16:12.940
Just the build, kind of.

16:13.859 --> 16:14.460
Mr. Xu,

16:14.460 --> 16:15.379
someone as disciplined as you

16:15.659 --> 16:16.820
would never drink that much.

16:17.259 --> 16:18.180
And even if you did,

16:18.379 --> 16:19.019
you wouldn't be

16:19.019 --> 16:19.779
acting like that.

16:29.619 --> 16:31.979
The video quality is pretty bad.

16:32.820 --> 16:34.540
You can't assume he's anyone

16:35.100 --> 16:36.180
just because he's in a suit.

16:37.139 --> 16:38.060
And a piece of advice,

16:38.300 --> 16:38.739
when you get home,

16:38.739 --> 16:39.700
tell your property management

16:39.700 --> 16:40.580
to step up security

16:40.580 --> 16:41.540
around the complex.

16:48.739 --> 16:49.499
That guy

16:49.899 --> 16:50.499
is probably

16:50.499 --> 16:51.619
a fan of Li Shican.

16:52.379 --> 16:53.340
Looks like he was dancing

16:53.940 --> 16:55.139
one of Li Shican's routines.

16:56.460 --> 16:57.700
But it was pretty ridiculous.

17:06.139 --> 17:06.940
Let's eat.

17:08.139 --> 17:08.779
The congee's getting cold.

17:15.980 --> 17:17.939
Li Shican dances well?

17:20.260 --> 17:21.260
Everyone has their specialty.

17:21.619 --> 17:22.100
He is

17:22.100 --> 17:23.260
a professional after all.

17:24.699 --> 17:26.459
Mr. Xu, you know Li Shican too?

17:28.419 --> 17:29.659
I should be asking you that.

17:30.619 --> 17:31.899
Who doesn't know a big star?

17:32.419 --> 17:33.820
But being able to sit

17:33.820 --> 17:35.100
under the same roof,

17:35.740 --> 17:36.939
on the same couch,

17:37.859 --> 17:39.260
you must be very close.

17:40.939 --> 17:41.820
You mean last time?

17:42.820 --> 17:43.500
I've known Li Shican

17:43.500 --> 17:44.780
since before he was famous.

17:44.980 --> 17:45.820
We were college classmates.

17:46.340 --> 17:46.899
Is that all?

17:49.100 --> 17:51.060
You're also townmates, right?

17:53.459 --> 17:54.419
I remember Li Shican

17:54.419 --> 17:55.740
is also from Su City.

17:56.980 --> 17:57.540
Yes.

17:58.859 --> 17:59.780
So you knew him in high school?

18:00.699 --> 18:01.379
Not exactly.

18:01.780 --> 18:02.820
He went to Su City No. 2 High.

18:03.020 --> 18:03.580
I went to...

18:07.540 --> 18:10.219
Which high school did you go to?

18:14.100 --> 18:14.500
I...

18:22.619 --> 18:23.300
I...

18:25.820 --> 18:26.859
Sorry, Mr. Xu.

18:26.859 --> 18:27.340
It's okay.

18:27.619 --> 18:28.179
Let me.

18:28.419 --> 18:29.219
-So sorry.
-No problem.

18:30.260 --> 18:31.179
Thanks.

18:40.060 --> 18:41.459
Mr. Xu, let's eat.

18:41.740 --> 18:42.379
The congee is getting cold.

19:01.500 --> 19:03.100
That cup of water

19:03.100 --> 19:04.580
did you a big favor.

19:05.219 --> 19:06.260
Stop laughing.

19:06.780 --> 19:08.020
Xu Huaisong had been

19:08.020 --> 19:09.300
abroad for years.

19:10.179 --> 19:11.100
How does he know

19:11.179 --> 19:12.459
Li Shican's from

19:12.459 --> 19:13.459
Su City?

19:14.179 --> 19:14.980
Is Li Shican

19:14.980 --> 19:16.020
that famous already?

19:16.540 --> 19:18.419
Not Li Shican's problem.

19:18.540 --> 19:20.139
You're the one who brought him up.

19:21.580 --> 19:22.980
But I do get the feeling

19:23.699 --> 19:24.820
that Xu Huaisong

19:25.340 --> 19:27.060
has some kind of issue with him.

19:27.820 --> 19:28.500
I know.

19:28.500 --> 19:29.139
It must be because

19:29.139 --> 19:30.340
of that misunderstanding last time.

19:30.939 --> 19:32.020
Didn't Xu Huaisong

19:32.020 --> 19:32.820
call the cops?

19:33.419 --> 19:34.060
True.

19:34.740 --> 19:36.179
But talking to Xu Huaisong

19:36.179 --> 19:37.100
is like walking

19:37.580 --> 19:39.340
through a minefield, filled with traps.

19:40.219 --> 19:40.859
I'd better avoid

19:41.260 --> 19:42.780
seeing him alone in the future.

19:43.379 --> 19:43.859
Otherwise, I'd

19:43.859 --> 19:44.859
slip up sooner or later.

19:48.699 --> 19:49.899
In my opinion,

19:49.899 --> 19:50.659
rather than

19:50.659 --> 19:51.899
being on edge

19:51.899 --> 19:52.859
all the time,

19:53.020 --> 19:54.219
you should just be brave

19:54.219 --> 19:55.260
and come clean.

19:55.980 --> 19:56.619
If you really

19:56.619 --> 19:58.179
don't care about Xu Huaisong anymore,

19:59.260 --> 20:00.740
just let it go

20:01.260 --> 20:03.260
and move on with your life.

20:03.980 --> 20:04.500
Okay?

20:06.219 --> 20:07.659
It's two completely

20:07.659 --> 20:09.020
different issues.

20:10.300 --> 20:11.179
I just don't want

20:11.179 --> 20:12.939
to rip off that last bit of dignity

20:13.179 --> 20:14.300
from my youth and leave it

20:14.300 --> 20:15.340
out in the open.

20:17.179 --> 20:18.100
It's too embarrassing.

20:40.419 --> 20:41.619
Mom, Dad, I'm home.

20:42.260 --> 20:43.219
Yu, you are back!

20:44.619 --> 20:45.580
Hold on. Let me turn it off.

20:48.100 --> 20:49.219
What's for dinner, Mom?

20:49.459 --> 20:50.540
Tomorrow's the winter solstice,

20:50.540 --> 20:50.899
so I'm

20:50.899 --> 20:51.780
making sweet rice balls.

20:51.780 --> 20:52.379
Your favorite.

20:53.020 --> 20:53.899
Awesome.

20:54.060 --> 20:55.219
I'm gonna have it

20:55.500 --> 20:56.980
with osmanthus wine.

20:57.139 --> 20:58.459
Of course. I know.

20:59.340 --> 21:00.260
Let me wash my hands and help.

21:01.379 --> 21:01.820
Come on.

21:01.820 --> 21:02.820
How are you going to help?

21:02.820 --> 21:03.899
You'll just get in the way.

21:03.899 --> 21:04.500
Right?

21:05.139 --> 21:06.219
Way to kill my enthusiasm.

21:07.859 --> 21:09.179
Mom, where's dad?

21:09.419 --> 21:09.899
Your dad?

21:09.899 --> 21:10.939
He was just here.

21:11.340 --> 21:12.379
-Yu, you are back!
-Dad.

21:14.300 --> 21:15.500
We're in for a treat.

21:16.020 --> 21:17.139
Thanks, honey.

21:17.939 --> 21:18.340
Come on,

21:18.459 --> 21:19.780
let's go get some sun in the yard.

21:21.219 --> 21:22.820
Mom, I'll go outside then.

21:22.980 --> 21:24.179
You two are really

21:24.179 --> 21:25.060
leaving me here alone?

21:31.540 --> 21:33.699
This weather is amazing.

21:34.459 --> 21:36.699
Have you talked to Liu Mao lately?

21:38.139 --> 21:39.060
Here we go again.

21:40.020 --> 21:41.340
I told you last time,

21:41.540 --> 21:42.659
we're not a good fit.

21:44.260 --> 21:45.260
Not to bug you,

21:45.740 --> 21:47.659
but being a lawyer is
a good profession.

21:48.219 --> 21:49.580
If you ever run into trouble,

21:49.859 --> 21:51.179
he can stand up for you.

21:52.340 --> 21:52.820
Dad,

21:53.260 --> 21:54.619
do you really want your daughter

21:54.619 --> 21:55.619
to run into trouble that badly?

21:56.020 --> 21:56.699
Silly girl.

21:57.219 --> 21:57.859
Can't you tell your dad's

21:57.859 --> 21:58.699
just worried about you?

21:58.980 --> 21:59.580
Exactly.

22:00.379 --> 22:00.699
Here.

22:02.020 --> 22:02.820
Oh, Yu,

22:03.300 --> 22:04.179
your mom and I are thinking

22:04.179 --> 22:05.580
about making a trip back to Su City.

22:06.980 --> 22:07.859
Don't.

22:08.780 --> 22:10.340
It's been so windy and rainy lately.

22:10.619 --> 22:11.340
Today's the only

22:11.340 --> 22:12.699
nice day we've had.

22:13.580 --> 22:14.179
If you take

22:14.179 --> 22:15.139
a trip now,

22:15.580 --> 22:16.580
your arthritis will act up.

22:16.939 --> 22:17.540
That house

22:17.540 --> 22:18.939
has been vacant for years,

22:19.020 --> 22:19.899
still needs a cleaning

22:20.060 --> 22:21.459
for the winter solstice.

22:21.459 --> 22:21.859
Right.

22:22.219 --> 22:23.699
And your mom's been

22:23.980 --> 22:25.260
wanting to go back anyway.

22:25.859 --> 22:26.459
Alright then.

22:27.139 --> 22:28.060
I'll go with mom.

22:28.580 --> 22:29.899
You stay home and rest.

22:30.619 --> 22:32.300
That way, mom and I can have

22:32.300 --> 22:33.459
some quality time together.

22:33.939 --> 22:35.379
You silly kid.

22:35.500 --> 22:36.580
Girls at your age

22:36.699 --> 22:38.060
all spend time with boyfriends.

22:38.060 --> 22:39.580
You want to hang out with your mom?

22:39.580 --> 22:40.379
Yes.

22:40.859 --> 22:41.300
Fine.

22:42.619 --> 22:43.300
I guess I'll just

22:43.740 --> 22:44.580
have to be okay with it.

22:45.980 --> 22:47.899
And I'm looking forward to it.

22:48.260 --> 22:49.580
Then I'll

22:50.699 --> 22:52.139
have to accept it.

22:53.740 --> 22:54.699
Alright.

22:56.179 --> 22:57.459
You two have your fun.

23:01.100 --> 23:02.540
The weather is so nice.

23:06.780 --> 23:09.060
Why don't you message Mao?

23:09.659 --> 23:10.619
Young people need

23:11.219 --> 23:12.699
to spend time together

23:12.899 --> 23:13.540
to have a chance

23:13.540 --> 23:14.780
of going further.

23:16.899 --> 23:18.459
Remember when we were young?

23:20.540 --> 23:21.619
If Yu had

23:21.980 --> 23:23.980
even half your skill,

23:24.379 --> 23:26.179
I wouldn't have to worry so much.

23:26.859 --> 23:27.659
Who does she take after?

23:30.939 --> 23:31.820
She takes after me.

23:46.500 --> 23:48.500
Mrs. Ruan just messaged me.

23:49.179 --> 23:50.699
She's still thinking about me,

23:50.699 --> 23:53.139
especially for an occasion like this.

23:56.260 --> 23:58.260
Looks like someone

23:58.260 --> 23:59.619
hasn't seen Ruan Yu

23:59.859 --> 24:00.980
in a while since

24:00.980 --> 24:02.419
the case prep.

24:03.060 --> 24:03.699
Makes sense.

24:04.340 --> 24:05.459
No chance to see her.

24:05.820 --> 24:06.619
Not like me,

24:06.780 --> 24:09.020
I got an invitation.

24:11.020 --> 24:11.820
My neck's

24:12.820 --> 24:14.379
been so stiff lately.

24:15.740 --> 24:17.179
Must be from overworking.

24:20.899 --> 24:21.659
Overworking, huh?

24:22.740 --> 24:23.740
Yeah, right there.

24:23.899 --> 24:24.580
A little harder.

24:27.780 --> 24:28.340
Here you go.

24:32.540 --> 24:33.659
Good technique.

24:34.179 --> 24:35.899
[Mao, you mentioned]

24:35.899 --> 24:37.540
[that you travel to Su City for work often.]

24:37.820 --> 24:38.379
[Do you have any plans]

24:38.379 --> 24:39.219
[to go there soon again?]

24:39.659 --> 24:40.300
[Maybe you could give]

24:40.300 --> 24:41.419
[Yu and me a ride to the old house]

24:41.419 --> 24:42.419
[to pick up some things?]

24:42.699 --> 24:43.260
[If it's too much trouble,]

24:43.260 --> 24:44.260
[don't worry about it.]

24:44.379 --> 24:45.060
[You can always come by]

24:45.060 --> 24:46.179
[for a meal some other time.]

24:46.580 --> 24:49.139
How about this, I'll let you

24:49.340 --> 24:50.899
make the decision.

24:52.139 --> 24:54.219
Just reply however you want.

24:55.020 --> 24:56.219
Just tell her

24:56.619 --> 24:57.340
I don't have time.

24:57.939 --> 24:59.020
Or tell her I'm not

24:59.260 --> 25:00.540
compatible with

25:00.740 --> 25:01.419
her daughter.

25:04.020 --> 25:05.300
I'm willing

25:05.899 --> 25:07.260
to sacrifice my good name

25:07.820 --> 25:08.859
for your happiness.

25:14.619 --> 25:15.419
There's something else.

25:16.859 --> 25:18.139
The matchmaking agency

25:18.139 --> 25:19.459
next to our office

25:19.580 --> 25:20.659
is closing next month.

25:20.980 --> 25:22.260
I was thinking

25:22.740 --> 25:23.619
we could rent it

25:24.219 --> 25:25.500
and expand

25:25.500 --> 25:26.859
our firm.

25:27.419 --> 25:28.859
Make it bigger and brighter.

25:31.139 --> 25:31.980
I'd be honored.

25:32.260 --> 25:33.300
I'll be out working on a case tomorrow.

25:33.300 --> 25:34.459
Tomorrow night's no good.

25:34.459 --> 25:35.340
I have a date.

25:36.820 --> 25:38.139
From that matchmaking agency?

25:39.899 --> 25:41.300
You sure a place

25:41.300 --> 25:42.659
that can't even pay rent can handle

25:42.659 --> 25:43.500
your happiness

25:43.500 --> 25:44.980
for the rest of your life?

25:49.580 --> 25:51.379
Rent runs on money.

25:52.020 --> 25:52.859
Love doesn't.

25:56.179 --> 25:56.820
Won't take much

25:56.820 --> 25:58.139
of your time tomorrow.

25:58.580 --> 25:59.540
And it definitely won't interfere

25:59.540 --> 26:00.619
with your date at night.

26:06.419 --> 26:07.219
[No wonder my mom wouldn't]

26:07.219 --> 26:08.340
[let me buy train tickets.]

26:08.980 --> 26:11.060
[If I'd known it was a ride like this...]

26:12.179 --> 26:13.340
Mr. Liu, sorry

26:13.619 --> 26:14.260
to trouble you.

26:14.699 --> 26:15.980
No trouble at all.

26:15.980 --> 26:16.740
It's on the way anyway.

26:19.540 --> 26:20.699
Are you really going

26:20.699 --> 26:21.619
to Su City for a case?

26:21.939 --> 26:23.379
Yeah. A site visit.

26:24.260 --> 26:26.740
An old classmate

26:27.580 --> 26:28.419
of a client

26:28.859 --> 26:29.899
happens to be in Su City.

26:30.459 --> 26:31.820
You even have to interview old classmates?

26:32.500 --> 26:33.580
That's rough.

26:34.659 --> 26:35.419
Tell me about it.

26:35.659 --> 26:37.379
Sometimes clients

26:38.500 --> 26:39.300
can be really difficult.

26:41.300 --> 26:41.939
Hey, Ruan Yu,

26:42.219 --> 26:42.939
I saw the house location

26:42.939 --> 26:44.020
you sent me.

26:44.659 --> 26:45.939
It's very close to Xu Huaisong's

26:45.939 --> 26:46.619
grandma's place.

26:47.260 --> 26:48.139
Xu Huaisong?

26:48.780 --> 26:49.459
[My mom taught]

26:49.459 --> 26:50.659
[Xu Huaisong Chinese for half a year.]

26:50.980 --> 26:52.179
[Would she still remember that?]

26:52.379 --> 26:53.300
[That'd blow my cover!]

26:54.139 --> 26:55.540
Really? What a coincidence.

26:56.060 --> 26:57.699
Mom, when we get there,

26:57.699 --> 26:59.139
do you want to try that...

26:59.219 --> 26:59.980
The name Xu Huaisong

26:59.980 --> 27:01.020
sounds so familiar.

27:01.540 --> 27:02.699
I can't remember at all.

27:03.260 --> 27:03.939
It's okay, Mrs. Ruan.

27:04.300 --> 27:06.219
Don't force yourself.

27:06.500 --> 27:07.500
It's not someone important.

27:08.219 --> 27:09.139
Just remember me.

27:09.659 --> 27:10.699
I remember you.

27:11.899 --> 27:12.859
I'm telling you,

27:13.060 --> 27:14.100
getting older

27:14.100 --> 27:14.980
is no joke.

27:15.300 --> 27:16.540
I used to remember

27:16.540 --> 27:17.619
every kid

27:17.859 --> 27:18.939
in the alleys

27:19.540 --> 27:20.699
and all my old students.

27:21.859 --> 27:22.899
Now, so many

27:22.899 --> 27:24.219
of them have slipped my mind.

27:25.580 --> 27:26.300
It's okay, Mom.

27:26.659 --> 27:28.179
My memory's not so great either.

27:28.820 --> 27:29.500
See? You should

27:30.139 --> 27:31.659
spend less time on the computer.

27:32.820 --> 27:33.899
You two keep chatting.

27:43.020 --> 27:43.820
So, I've safely

27:44.060 --> 27:45.060
delivered Yu

27:45.060 --> 27:46.619
and her mother.

27:46.780 --> 27:47.500
You can rest easy.

27:48.219 --> 27:49.020
Also,

27:49.619 --> 27:51.260
got some intel for you.

27:52.379 --> 27:53.340
In the car,

27:53.340 --> 27:54.219
I heard Mrs. Ruan say

27:54.219 --> 27:55.100
she's going back today

27:55.100 --> 27:56.219
to meet up with some old colleagues.

27:56.699 --> 27:57.459
Not sure if Ruan Yu

27:57.459 --> 27:58.780
will stop by the school.

27:59.179 --> 28:00.659
Something to think about.

28:06.419 --> 28:07.340
Liu, the wingman,

28:07.580 --> 28:08.659
mission accomplished!

28:15.100 --> 28:16.139
Mom, it's raining.

28:17.379 --> 28:17.859
Use the umbrella.

28:22.340 --> 28:23.500
See? I told you.

28:23.659 --> 28:24.500
Young as you are,

28:24.899 --> 28:25.859
sitting at the computer

28:25.859 --> 28:26.419
all day, and you

28:26.980 --> 28:28.419
get back pain at the slightest movement.

28:28.619 --> 28:29.139
What?

28:29.300 --> 28:30.379
Are you as old as I am now?

28:32.419 --> 28:34.540
Message received.

28:34.859 --> 28:36.540
I'll start working out.

28:37.939 --> 28:38.459
Take a look.

28:39.740 --> 28:42.060
Appreciate it while we can.

28:46.379 --> 28:47.300
I just can't bear

28:47.300 --> 28:48.179
to part with these

28:48.340 --> 28:49.340
old houses and flowers.

28:50.100 --> 28:50.980
Back in the day,

28:51.699 --> 28:52.419
your father and I

28:52.419 --> 28:53.419
got married here.

28:54.899 --> 28:55.820
You used to run all over

28:55.820 --> 28:56.939
playing here when you

28:57.060 --> 28:57.580
were little.

28:57.580 --> 28:58.260
Remember?

28:58.340 --> 28:59.340
I loved going there.

29:00.260 --> 29:01.379
And you were chased by two dogs,

29:01.379 --> 29:01.899
remember?

29:05.379 --> 29:06.100
Come to think of it,

29:06.379 --> 29:07.060
your grandparents

29:07.980 --> 29:09.139
were still around back then.

29:12.859 --> 29:13.379
Mom,

29:14.139 --> 29:15.740
the memories are still

29:16.219 --> 29:17.100
here with us.

29:18.300 --> 29:19.020
You know,

29:19.459 --> 29:20.139
we'll have fewer and fewer

29:20.139 --> 29:21.100
chances to come back.

29:22.139 --> 29:23.139
That's not true.

29:23.459 --> 29:24.980
Transportation is so easy now.

29:25.260 --> 29:26.780
I'll get a driver's license.

29:27.260 --> 29:28.699
If you and dad want to come back,

29:28.939 --> 29:29.459
I can give you

29:29.459 --> 29:30.260
a ride anytime.

29:30.859 --> 29:32.459
It's tiring for you to drive that long.

29:32.820 --> 29:33.740
It'd be best

29:34.260 --> 29:35.419
if my son-in-law

29:35.419 --> 29:36.740
did the driving.

29:37.260 --> 29:38.020
Mom,

29:39.139 --> 29:40.859
why do you bring that up again?

29:41.939 --> 29:42.859
I didn't want to

29:42.859 --> 29:43.820
say anything in the car.

29:44.340 --> 29:45.340
Actually, Mr. Liu

29:45.699 --> 29:46.179
already has

29:46.179 --> 29:47.540
a matchmaking date.

29:47.899 --> 29:48.619
So, don't go

29:48.899 --> 29:50.379
bothering him again.

29:51.219 --> 29:52.060
Really?

29:53.340 --> 29:54.419
I thought he seemed

29:54.419 --> 29:55.340
kinda interested.

29:55.340 --> 29:56.139
I thought...

29:57.379 --> 29:58.980
You already asked him,

29:59.139 --> 30:00.179
and he's

30:00.179 --> 30:01.540
a helpful person.

30:01.820 --> 30:03.260
How could he say no?

30:03.899 --> 30:05.219
Now I feel bad.

30:05.740 --> 30:07.020
Alright, it's fine.

30:07.619 --> 30:08.419
If he's taken,

30:08.659 --> 30:09.459
there'll be someone else.

30:10.060 --> 30:10.980
I'll keep looking for you.

30:11.260 --> 30:12.020
Alright,

30:12.260 --> 30:13.580
you take your time.

30:14.020 --> 30:15.899
I'm going to go get some water.

30:16.899 --> 30:17.419
Go ahead.

30:18.580 --> 30:19.780
Let me enjoy the view.

30:19.939 --> 30:20.580
Sure, Mom.

30:21.100 --> 30:21.619
Sir.

30:22.580 --> 30:23.179
What do you need?

30:23.939 --> 30:24.459
Soy sauce.

30:24.899 --> 30:25.379
Over there.

30:33.580 --> 30:34.060
Sir,

30:34.780 --> 30:35.699
which of these two

30:35.699 --> 30:37.020
is better for stir-fry?

30:38.060 --> 30:38.859
The Ruan family, right?

30:39.300 --> 30:40.540
Your parents use this one for stir-fry.

30:40.659 --> 30:41.859
This one works too.

30:42.300 --> 30:43.899
What about for a dipping sauce?

30:43.899 --> 30:45.179
Which is better?

30:45.459 --> 30:46.699
For dipping, let's see.

30:47.260 --> 30:47.659
This one.

30:47.980 --> 30:48.699
This works.

30:49.540 --> 30:50.780
Is it just for dipping?

30:51.020 --> 30:52.219
Can I use it for cold dishes?

30:52.540 --> 30:53.219
Sure.

30:53.659 --> 30:55.020
You can use both for cold dishes.

30:56.619 --> 30:57.060
So...

30:58.139 --> 30:59.100
which of these two

30:59.100 --> 31:00.300
is a better value?

31:00.619 --> 31:02.740
Which one won't stick to the pan?

31:03.419 --> 31:04.540
Let me take another look.

31:05.060 --> 31:05.619
Thanks.

31:10.740 --> 31:11.820
He finally looked at me.

31:16.179 --> 31:17.219
But why does he

31:18.060 --> 31:19.740
look at me like I'm an idiot?

31:30.260 --> 31:31.139
Ten years.

31:32.300 --> 31:33.219
Everything's changed.

31:36.740 --> 31:37.820
Done yet?

31:39.580 --> 31:40.219
Yes.

31:41.260 --> 31:42.300
Sir, I'll take this one.

31:44.659 --> 31:45.540
Coming, Mom.

31:51.980 --> 31:53.100
It cleared up!

31:53.419 --> 31:54.580
That's just how it is down south.

31:54.820 --> 31:55.899
On and off.

31:56.740 --> 31:57.580
It's almost noon.

31:57.580 --> 31:58.699
Let's go grab something to eat.

31:58.899 --> 31:59.419
Sounds good.

31:59.580 --> 32:00.219
What do you want?

32:01.260 --> 32:01.699
You pick.

32:01.699 --> 32:02.340
I'm fine with anything.

32:03.820 --> 32:04.740
In that case,

32:05.260 --> 32:06.580
I'm kinda craving the dishes from

32:06.580 --> 32:07.219
the school cafeteria.

32:09.379 --> 32:11.500
Going to the school cafeteria at noon,

32:11.859 --> 32:12.780
I'll run right

32:12.780 --> 32:13.619
into Xu Huaishi.

32:14.260 --> 32:14.659
Mom,

32:15.260 --> 32:16.340
let's go to that

32:16.340 --> 32:17.300
Zhou's Steak House.

32:17.500 --> 32:18.260
I've been craving it.

32:18.419 --> 32:19.820
You said you were fine with anything.

32:20.219 --> 32:21.300
The more I think about it,

32:21.300 --> 32:22.540
the more I crave those

32:22.540 --> 32:23.780
meatballs from the cafeteria.

32:23.780 --> 32:24.540
They are so good.

32:24.939 --> 32:25.580
And I can

32:26.260 --> 32:27.780
go catch up with

32:27.780 --> 32:28.740
Ms. Guo and Ms. Li.

32:29.619 --> 32:30.699
So looking forward to it.

32:31.179 --> 32:32.340
It's settled. Let's go.

32:33.580 --> 32:34.419
Little foodie.

32:34.659 --> 32:35.500
Eat your jelly.

32:37.340 --> 32:39.139
Let's hit the cafeteria.

32:39.740 --> 32:40.540
Grab the umbrella.

32:41.100 --> 32:41.619
It might

32:41.619 --> 32:42.340
rain again.

32:42.580 --> 32:43.379
That's right.

32:43.379 --> 32:43.820
Let's go.

32:53.219 --> 32:54.419
Being young is great.

32:55.219 --> 32:55.859
I always thought

32:55.859 --> 32:57.340
the uniform was ugly before.

32:57.820 --> 32:59.740
Now I don't even get a chance to wear one.

33:00.699 --> 33:01.540
If you're not young anymore,

33:01.540 --> 33:02.179
what does that make me?

33:03.179 --> 33:05.020
Mom, you're young.

33:05.179 --> 33:06.300
We're both young.

33:06.859 --> 33:07.899
Tell you what,

33:08.100 --> 33:08.659
how about I go borrow

33:08.659 --> 33:10.020
two uniforms from them?

33:10.020 --> 33:10.740
We can change into them.

33:10.939 --> 33:11.500
Maybe someone will

33:11.500 --> 33:12.179
come up and ask,

33:12.580 --> 33:13.020
"Excuse me,

33:13.419 --> 33:14.459
how do I get to the art gallery?"

33:16.540 --> 33:17.419
What did I teach you?

33:18.100 --> 33:19.060
Sharp tongue.

33:19.379 --> 33:20.699
No shame.

33:20.859 --> 33:21.459
Well said.

33:23.659 --> 33:25.260
Ma'am, I'll take three drumsticks.

33:25.659 --> 33:26.699
-Alright.
-Hungry?

33:30.340 --> 33:30.899
Ma'am,

33:32.020 --> 33:33.340
is Mr. Cai

33:33.340 --> 33:34.459
still working here?

33:35.379 --> 33:36.139
Which Mr. Cai?

33:36.379 --> 33:37.100
The one

33:37.100 --> 33:38.179
who used to

33:38.179 --> 33:38.899
update the menu.

33:41.139 --> 33:41.780
Not ringing a bell.

33:42.859 --> 33:43.540
Ms. Zhu,

33:44.580 --> 33:45.659
I'm Mrs. Ruan.

33:45.740 --> 33:46.619
Nice to see you.

33:46.619 --> 33:47.459
Give me two more vegetable dishes.

33:47.540 --> 33:48.300
Okay.

33:50.219 --> 33:50.859
Since we're here,

33:51.340 --> 33:52.659
make up for all the drumsticks

33:52.899 --> 33:53.820
I didn't get to eat back then.

33:55.300 --> 33:56.020
Yum!

33:56.379 --> 33:56.899
Good, huh?

33:59.060 --> 34:00.379
Huaishi, we're leaving.

34:06.100 --> 34:06.459
Brother,

34:07.780 --> 34:08.459
right here.

34:16.020 --> 34:16.540
What's wrong?

34:17.420 --> 34:18.940
Mom, you eat more.

34:19.339 --> 34:20.259
You'd look better with some weight.

34:20.659 --> 34:21.420
You just said

34:21.420 --> 34:22.420
you were hungry and wanted

34:23.020 --> 34:23.619
three drumsticks.

34:24.020 --> 34:25.020
Lost your appetite already?

34:25.339 --> 34:25.860
How can I finish

34:25.860 --> 34:26.739
three all by myself?

34:27.259 --> 34:29.179
[Why is Xu Huaisong here?]

34:29.860 --> 34:30.739
[I just dodged]

34:30.739 --> 34:31.659
[his questions last time.]

34:32.699 --> 34:33.659
[If he sees me sitting]

34:33.659 --> 34:35.179
[in the No.1 High cafeteria,]

34:35.980 --> 34:36.819
[across from]

34:36.819 --> 34:38.500
[his old Chinese teacher.]

34:39.779 --> 34:40.460
[He's going to figure out]

34:40.460 --> 34:41.219
[I went to No.1 High.]

34:42.259 --> 34:43.139
[Then he'll ask me]

34:43.500 --> 34:44.580
[what year, what class.]

34:45.380 --> 34:47.380
[He might remember something he shouldn't.]

34:50.500 --> 34:51.420
You know,

34:51.980 --> 34:53.060
back when I was young,

34:54.339 --> 34:55.219
your father said

34:56.179 --> 34:57.259
I looked like Xue Baochai.

34:57.779 --> 34:58.860
I'll send you the revisions

34:58.860 --> 34:59.460
later.

35:00.060 --> 35:01.659
Okay, bye.

35:03.380 --> 35:05.179
Brother, why are you suddenly back?

35:05.500 --> 35:06.500
Felt like it.

35:07.139 --> 35:08.980
Let's go have hot pot

35:09.420 --> 35:10.460
for winter solstice tonight.

35:10.460 --> 35:10.860
How about it?

35:11.139 --> 35:11.699
Tonight?

35:12.540 --> 35:12.980
I'm busy.

35:13.580 --> 35:14.179
Liar.

35:14.739 --> 35:15.619
You're clearly free.

35:15.619 --> 35:16.540
You're watching me eat.

35:18.100 --> 35:19.420
Who said I came to see you?

35:22.460 --> 35:23.420
Do you have another

35:23.420 --> 35:24.339
sister at No.1 High?

35:28.380 --> 35:29.380
Stop looking around.

35:29.819 --> 35:30.619
Just eat.

35:35.580 --> 35:36.339
It's really good.

35:39.460 --> 35:40.259
I'm leaving.

35:42.139 --> 35:43.860
So soon?

35:44.540 --> 35:45.540
Go back to class after lunch.

35:45.540 --> 35:46.420
Get some rest.

35:47.659 --> 35:48.980
Wait for me.

35:52.739 --> 35:53.299
Yu,

35:53.699 --> 35:54.299
I'm going to see

35:54.299 --> 35:55.060
Ms. Li later.

35:55.179 --> 35:56.139
You go take a walk around.

36:02.060 --> 36:02.580
It's good?

36:04.339 --> 36:05.299
I'll have one.

36:05.540 --> 36:06.500
There you go.

36:06.860 --> 36:08.339
Just eat it if you want.

36:09.900 --> 36:10.900
Knew you couldn't resist.

36:16.219 --> 36:16.819
Down low.

36:20.219 --> 36:20.940
Pass it to me.

36:23.179 --> 36:23.580
Come on.

36:23.940 --> 36:24.860
Defense! Defense!

36:28.819 --> 36:29.580
Left foot, go.

36:30.100 --> 36:30.500
Nice.

36:30.500 --> 36:32.699
[December 21st. Winter Solstice.]

36:33.100 --> 36:34.060
[Sunny.]

36:34.580 --> 36:36.540
[Today I went back to Su City No.1 High.]

36:37.860 --> 36:38.339
Watch out.

36:40.060 --> 36:40.940
You okay, Miss?

36:41.500 --> 36:42.020
I'm fine.

36:42.619 --> 36:43.900
Did I bother your writing?

36:44.540 --> 36:46.219
No, just jotting in my journal.

36:46.380 --> 36:47.179
Don't worry about it.

36:47.940 --> 36:48.619
People still

36:48.619 --> 36:49.980
write in journals these days?

36:51.139 --> 36:52.380
Just jotting down life.

36:54.659 --> 36:55.460
That's so artistic.

36:56.540 --> 36:57.540
Are you a writer or something?

36:58.980 --> 36:59.739
I guess

37:01.100 --> 37:02.619
you could call me a writer.

37:02.940 --> 37:03.779
What do you write?

37:07.299 --> 37:08.060
Romance novels.

37:13.779 --> 37:15.540
So you must be good at dating.

37:18.460 --> 37:21.060
Shouldn't you be focusing

37:21.060 --> 37:22.339
on your studies right now

37:22.659 --> 37:23.580
instead of dating?

37:26.380 --> 37:26.980
Adults say

37:26.980 --> 37:28.100
we can't date

37:28.500 --> 37:29.659
because it'll affect

37:29.659 --> 37:30.500
our grades.

37:32.020 --> 37:33.020
My grades

37:34.460 --> 37:35.940
can't get any lower.

37:38.940 --> 37:40.219
The way you put it is quite...

37:40.219 --> 37:40.779
Honest.

37:42.500 --> 37:43.739
If you can't have good grades,

37:43.739 --> 37:44.699
at least have a good attitude.

37:45.179 --> 37:46.259
If you had neither,

37:46.980 --> 37:47.819
that would really suck.

37:50.980 --> 37:51.980
So does the person you like

37:51.980 --> 37:52.659
like you back?

37:57.980 --> 37:58.940
Like?

38:00.219 --> 38:01.179
I'd be grateful if she

38:02.060 --> 38:03.380
went one day without hitting me.

38:03.860 --> 38:04.860
So that means

38:05.540 --> 38:07.940
you've got

38:08.980 --> 38:09.500
a crush.

38:15.940 --> 38:16.779
Wouldn't have guessed.

38:17.500 --> 38:18.339
Someone like you

38:18.339 --> 38:19.139
having a crush?

38:21.060 --> 38:22.659
Even the most carefree person

38:22.860 --> 38:24.259
gets a little nervous

38:24.259 --> 38:25.540
around the one they like.

38:27.219 --> 38:28.540
Everyone just shows it

38:28.540 --> 38:29.259
differently.

38:31.739 --> 38:32.420
That's true.

38:34.179 --> 38:35.259
So can you tell me

38:35.739 --> 38:36.380
what I should do

38:36.380 --> 38:37.179
when I like someone?

38:40.100 --> 38:41.420
I can teach you

38:41.420 --> 38:42.380
how to get better at Chinese.

38:42.659 --> 38:43.500
I was really good at Chinese

38:43.500 --> 38:44.299
back in the day.

38:44.500 --> 38:44.980
What do you say?

38:47.819 --> 38:48.739
Adults are

38:49.339 --> 38:49.980
so boring.

38:51.659 --> 38:52.580
What's your name?

38:52.860 --> 38:53.580
Zhao Yi.

38:54.500 --> 38:55.380
It's Yi,

38:55.540 --> 38:56.259
not Tie.

39:10.259 --> 39:11.100
Tell her

39:12.219 --> 39:13.100
how you feel

39:14.179 --> 39:15.299
on graduation day.

39:45.739 --> 39:46.380
Mr. Liu.

39:47.299 --> 39:47.819
Ruan Yu.

39:48.699 --> 39:49.460
Sorry,

39:49.460 --> 39:50.540
something came up.

39:50.699 --> 39:51.860
During my site visit,

39:51.860 --> 39:52.299
I ran into two

39:52.299 --> 39:53.179
important clients. I need to

39:53.659 --> 39:55.179
drive them back to Hang City tonight,

39:55.299 --> 39:56.339
so I might not be able to...

39:56.900 --> 39:57.500
Don't worry.

39:57.699 --> 39:58.779
I'll just get two high-speed

39:58.779 --> 39:59.819
train tickets.

40:00.219 --> 40:00.739
Don't

40:00.980 --> 40:01.819
book tickets yet.

40:02.380 --> 40:03.139
There's still

40:03.179 --> 40:04.500
one seat available in my car.

40:04.500 --> 40:05.460
I can drive

40:06.259 --> 40:06.940
your mom back.

40:06.940 --> 40:08.339
It'll be more comfortable for her.

40:08.739 --> 40:09.860
Just be careful

40:09.860 --> 40:11.179
on your way back, okay?

40:11.739 --> 40:12.179
Okay.

40:12.380 --> 40:13.460
Thanks, Mr. Liu.

40:13.739 --> 40:14.540
No problem.

40:14.540 --> 40:15.219
Alright then.

40:15.500 --> 40:15.940
Bye.

40:16.179 --> 40:16.779
Bye.

40:17.900 --> 40:18.659
Sorry about that.

40:19.020 --> 40:19.580
Mr. Liu,

40:19.860 --> 40:21.060
we don't want to trouble you.

40:21.380 --> 40:22.100
We can just take

40:22.100 --> 40:22.779
the train back.

40:23.139 --> 40:23.659
It's okay.

40:23.659 --> 40:24.819
No trouble at all.

40:24.980 --> 40:25.540
And my boss

40:25.540 --> 40:26.460
insisted that

40:26.779 --> 40:27.460
you two

40:27.659 --> 40:28.739
ride back with me.

40:29.540 --> 40:30.020
Well...

40:32.339 --> 40:32.779
Okay.

40:42.179 --> 40:44.460
Sir, how cheap is "a steal"?

40:45.819 --> 40:46.619
You are finally here!

40:47.179 --> 40:48.060
Any later,

40:48.179 --> 40:48.699
I couldn't have held onto

40:48.699 --> 40:49.699
the good stuff any longer.

40:50.940 --> 40:52.100
You've been waiting for me?

40:52.219 --> 40:53.179
Is it because I'm the only one

40:53.420 --> 40:54.380
who wants to buy it?

40:54.779 --> 40:55.699
Of course not.

40:55.940 --> 40:56.779
As you know, we've been

40:56.779 --> 40:57.860
here for years,

40:59.060 --> 40:59.739
That guy also

41:00.060 --> 41:01.060
came by a while back.

41:01.460 --> 41:02.020
Which guy?

41:02.779 --> 41:03.380
You know,

41:05.179 --> 41:05.819
that one.

41:06.259 --> 41:06.699
Oh,

41:07.060 --> 41:07.699
the one who

41:07.699 --> 41:08.619
fought you over Galactic Empire.

41:09.179 --> 41:09.739
Remember?

41:11.420 --> 41:12.699
Who?

41:14.020 --> 41:14.819
Can't remember.

41:16.659 --> 41:17.779
Alright, take a look around.

41:18.020 --> 41:18.860
We'll catch up later.

41:19.139 --> 41:19.580
Okay.

41:20.100 --> 41:20.860
Talk later, Sir.

41:20.860 --> 41:21.500
Okay.

41:37.139 --> 41:39.339
See what I need.

42:09.020 --> 42:10.779
June 2013.

42:12.540 --> 42:13.139
That was the month

42:13.139 --> 42:14.259
I was about to become a senior.

42:16.380 --> 42:18.259
Sir, I'll take this one too.

42:19.060 --> 42:19.540
Okay.

42:20.219 --> 42:20.860
Here you go.

42:36.739 --> 42:37.299
Zhao Yi,

42:38.020 --> 42:38.739
you're not coming?

42:40.900 --> 42:41.699
I'll catch you guys later.

42:42.020 --> 42:43.259
Alright, let's go.

42:58.139 --> 42:59.100
What's your name?

42:59.139 --> 43:00.819
We're not in the same class.

43:00.819 --> 43:02.619
I was worried all break.

43:03.299 --> 43:05.060
Siyu, she picked Liberal Arts,

43:05.420 --> 43:06.659
but she's not in our class.

43:06.739 --> 43:08.020
She got put in Class Five.

43:08.299 --> 43:09.299
So we're not together?

43:09.299 --> 43:10.500
I don't know why.

43:11.139 --> 43:11.739
Everyone has their

43:11.739 --> 43:13.380
strengths and weaknesses.

43:14.339 --> 43:15.259
I'm not following the crowd.

43:15.739 --> 43:16.699
My passion isn't in Sciences.

43:17.139 --> 43:18.659
I'll go for

43:18.659 --> 43:19.460
Liberal Arts.

43:25.020 --> 43:25.900
Not too bad.

43:25.900 --> 43:27.179
Now we're deskmates.

43:27.179 --> 43:28.420
We can always go find her.

43:29.299 --> 43:30.460
What do you want for dinner tonight?

43:30.860 --> 43:31.739
Hello, class.

43:32.060 --> 43:32.940
Take your seats.

43:34.980 --> 43:35.860
The Chinese class rep.

43:36.380 --> 43:36.940
Here.

43:37.540 --> 43:38.860
Let's take attendance

43:38.860 --> 43:39.819
and get to know each other.

43:41.619 --> 43:42.179
Ms.

43:46.060 --> 43:47.060
Chen Yan.

43:47.299 --> 43:47.779
Here.

43:49.380 --> 43:50.699
Wang Haolin.

43:50.819 --> 43:51.259
Here.

43:52.980 --> 43:54.060
Zhao Tie.

43:57.779 --> 43:58.860
Zhao Tie.

44:01.980 --> 44:02.860
Zhao Tie.

44:03.020 --> 44:03.699
Excuse me.

44:04.219 --> 44:05.100
You're the Chinese rep.

44:05.100 --> 44:05.819
Can't you read?

44:06.060 --> 44:06.980
Is that "Tie"?

44:07.860 --> 44:08.659
That's Yi.

44:08.779 --> 44:09.619
Y-I, Yi.

44:12.819 --> 44:13.540
What?

44:14.060 --> 44:15.380
Chinese reps

44:15.380 --> 44:16.139
can't be nearsighted?

44:24.299 --> 44:25.619
What are you thinking, Zhao Tie?

44:25.619 --> 44:26.219
You spacing out?

44:31.540 --> 44:32.500
Zhao Yi.

44:33.060 --> 44:33.580
Mr. Zhao.

44:34.420 --> 44:35.779
You know, because of you,

44:36.139 --> 44:36.619
my name was

44:36.619 --> 44:37.619
mispronounced for almost a year.

44:38.060 --> 44:39.460
It's too late to fix it now.

44:40.739 --> 44:41.980
Where are you going?

44:41.980 --> 44:43.060
I need to study, okay?

44:43.779 --> 44:45.659
Listen to yourself.

44:45.659 --> 44:46.659
I don't buy it.

45:01.540 --> 45:02.900
Sir, I'm leaving.

45:03.580 --> 45:04.179
Okay.

45:16.659 --> 45:17.339
Yu,

45:17.619 --> 45:18.500
I'm in Mao's

45:18.500 --> 45:19.540
car now.

45:19.699 --> 45:20.940
Take care and be careful.

45:21.100 --> 45:21.980
Keep me posted.

46:49.299 --> 46:49.980
Who are you?

46:50.580 --> 46:51.619
I don't add strangers.

46:55.380 --> 46:56.699
I'm the new cafeteria contractor.

46:57.060 --> 46:58.380
If there's anything you want to eat,

46:58.380 --> 46:59.060
let me know.

46:59.699 --> 47:00.219
My name is Cai.

47:03.580 --> 47:04.540
No wonder they had

47:04.540 --> 47:05.339
the class reps collect

47:05.339 --> 47:06.339
everyone's QQ numbers.

47:06.940 --> 47:08.339
You guys are really on top of things.

47:09.299 --> 47:10.659
You should make more drumsticks.

47:10.980 --> 47:12.420
They're always gone when I get there.

47:14.739 --> 47:15.259
You got it.
